        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">How far in advance should I book?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We recommend booking at least 24 hours in advance for best availability, though we can often accommodate same-day requests.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Do you track flights?</h3>
